movies.title: Rasputin
movies.plot: Into an era seething with war and revolution, a man comes with an incredible power to heal a nation...or destroy it. Based on the true story of one of the most powerful and mysterious figures in Russian history.
movies.awards: Won 3 Golden Globes. Another 5 wins & 11 nominations.
